snippet.title: Ib - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Ib is coming to Nintendo Switch in Spring 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/ib-switch/

A young girl named Ib visits an art gallery with her parents. While perusing the various works of art, Ib suddenly realizes that she is alone. As she searches for someone – anyone – else, the museum begins to change…

#Ib #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch
